***
### Tender Announcement
#### Contract: T3033-2424V8 - Electric Tractor

**Reference Number:** WS4566336602
**Solicitation Number:** WS4566336602

**Notice Type:** Request for Proposal
**Procurement Method:** Competitive - Open Bidding

**Release Date:** 2024-05-06
**Tender Closing Date:** 2024-06-05 at 14:00:00

**Contract Value:** Not disclosed

**Procurement Category:** Goods Delivery

**Trade Agreements:** This procurement is governed by the Canada-Ukraine Free Trade Agreement (CUFTA), Canada-European Union Comprehensive Economic and Trade Agreement (CETA), Canada-Chile Free Trade Agreement (CCFTA), Canada-Korea Free Trade Agreement (CKFTA), World Trade Organization Agreement on Government Procurement (WTO GPA), Canadian Free Trade Agreement (CFTA), Canada-Peru Free Trade Agreement (CPFTA), Canada-Honduras Free Trade Agreement, Canada-UK Trade Continuity Agreement (Canada-UK TCA), Canada-Colombia Free Trade Agreement, and Comprehensive and Progressive Agreement for Trans-Pacific Partnership (CPTPP).

**Contract Description:**

Department of Public Works and Government Services (PSPC) on behalf of the Department of Transport (TC) is soliciting proposals to purchase an electric tractor, including manuals and maintenance data sheets, training, an extended 24-month warranty, and delivery, located in Sept-Iles, Quebec, Canada.

**Contracting Entity Details:**

* Contracting entity name: Department of Public Works and Government Services (PSPC)
* Contract address: 11 Laurier St, Phase III, Place du Portage, Gatineau, QC, K1A 0S5
* Phone: (no phone nr)
